//- Return Policy Page
extends layout

block content
  .container.mt-5.fade-in
    .row.justify-content-center
      .col-lg-9
        .card.shadow-lg.mb-4.animated-card
          .card-body
            h1.mb-3.text-primary.text-center Return Policy
            .mb-4.text-center
              i.bi.bi-arrow-repeat.display-4.text-warning
            .mb-4
              .alert.alert-info.text-center.fade-in-quick
                | We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. Please read our return policy in detail below.
            .row
              .col-md-6.mb-4
                .card.border-0.bg-light.animated-card
                  .card-body
                    h3.text-secondary Eligibility for Returns
                    ul.list-group.list-group-flush
                      li.list-group-item.bg-transparent Most items can be returned within 14 days of delivery. Please initiate your return request within this period to be eligible for a refund or exchange.
                      li.list-group-item.bg-transparent Items must be unused, in original packaging, and with all tags attached.
                      li.list-group-item.bg-transparent Receipt or proof of purchase is required for all returns. If you have lost your receipt, please contact support for further assistance.
              .col-md-6.mb-4
                .card.border-0.bg-light.animated-card
                  .card-body
                    h3.text-secondary Non-Returnable Items
                    ul.list-group.list-group-flush
                      li.list-group-item.bg-transparent Perishable goods (food, treats) cannot be returned for safety and hygiene reasons.
                      li.list-group-item.bg-transparent Personalized or custom-made products are final sale and cannot be returned unless they arrive damaged or defective.
                      li.list-group-item.bg-transparent Gift cards are non-refundable and cannot be exchanged for cash or credit.
            .row
              .col-md-12.mb-4
                .card.border-0.bg-light.animated-card
                  .card-body
                    h3.text-secondary Return Process
                    ol.list-group.list-group-numbered
                      li.list-group-item.bg-transparent Contact our support team at 
                        a(href="mailto:gulbano7060@gmail.com") gulbano7060@gmail.com for a return authorization. Please provide your order number, item details, and reason for return.
                      li.list-group-item.bg-transparent Carefully pack your item and ship it to the address provided by our support team. Use a trackable shipping method to ensure safe delivery.
                      li.list-group-item.bg-transparent Once your return is received and inspected, we will notify you by email about your refund or exchange. If your return is approved, your refund will be processed within 7 business days.
            .row
              .col-md-6.mb-4
                .card.border-0.bg-light.animated-card
                  .card-body
                    h3.text-secondary Refunds
                    p.mb-0 Approved refunds will be processed to your original payment method within 7 business days after inspection. Shipping fees are non-refundable unless the return is due to our error or a defective product.
              .col-md-6.mb-4
                .card.border-0.bg-light.animated-card
                  .card-body
                    h3.text-secondary Exchanges
                    p.mb-0 If you need to exchange an item, please mention this in your return request. Exchanges are subject to product availability and can only be processed for items of equal or lesser value.
            .row
              .col-md-12.mb-2
                .card.border-0.bg-light.animated-card
                  .card-body
                    h3.text-secondary Questions?
                    p.mb-0 For any questions regarding returns, please contact our support team at 
                      a(href="mailto:gulbano7060@gmail.com") gulbano7060@gmail.com
                    p.text-muted.small.mt-2
                      | Our team is available to answer any questions you may have about the return policy, eligibility, or process. We are committed to ensuring your satisfaction and will do our best to resolve any concerns quickly and efficiently.

